[["Map",1,2,33,34],"blog",["Map",3,4],"how-to-download-youtube-shorts",{"id":3,"data":5,"body":11,"filePath":12,"digest":13,"rendered":14},{"title":6,"description":7,"pubDate":8,"heroImage":9,"category":10},"How to Download YouTube Shorts: The Ultimate 2024 Guide","Learn the fastest and easiest ways to save YouTube Shorts directly to your mobile device or computer for free.",["Date","2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z"],"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611162617474-5b21e879e113?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop","Tutorial","YouTube Shorts are taking over the platform. But how do you save them for offline viewing? \r\n\r\nIn this guide, we'll show you exactly how to use **VideoDL Pro** to grab any Shorts link and convert it to a high-quality MP4 file in seconds.\r\n\r\n## Step 1: Copy the Link\r\nFind the Short you want to download and click the 'Share' button to copy the URL.\r\n\r\n## Step 2: Paste into VideoDL Pro\r\nHead over to our homepage and paste the link into the magic 3D box.\r\n\r\n## Step 3: Choose Your Quality\r\nSelect from 720p or 1080p (if available) and hit download!","src/content/blog/how-to-download-youtube-shorts.md","b5812a1539a7bec5",{"html":15,"metadata":16},"\u003Cp>YouTube Shorts are taking over the platform. But how do you save them for offline viewing?\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>In this guide, we’ll show you exactly how to use \u003Cstrong>VideoDL Pro\u003C/strong> to grab any Shorts link and convert it to a high-quality MP4 file in seconds.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"step-1-copy-the-link\">Step 1: Copy the Link\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Find the Short you want to download and click the ‘Share’ button to copy the URL.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"step-2-paste-into-videodl-pro\">Step 2: Paste into VideoDL Pro\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Head over to our homepage and paste the link into the magic 3D box.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"step-3-choose-your-quality\">Step 3: Choose Your Quality\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Select from 720p or 1080p (if available) and hit download!\u003C/p>",{"headings"